(496, 6, 'idpaquete', '48', '48,Escape a Tarapoto,04,03,<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; list-style: outside none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Con este paquete turístico visitará los&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">4 lugares turísticos de Tarapoto</span>&nbsp;más conocidos: la Laguna Azul, Alto Mayo, Lamas y Catarata de Ahuashiyacu.</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Conocerá el único castillo de estilo medieval de toda la amazonía, el&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Castillo de Lamas.</span></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Podrá bañarse en las cálidas aguas de la&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">laguna azul</span>&nbsp;(20º de media) y navegar en bote.</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Tendrá la posibilidad de conocer la zona de&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Moyobamba y Rioja</span>&nbsp;y disfrutar de algunos de los rincones más bellos de la selva alta Peruana.</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Por último conocerá la catarata más importante y emblemática de San Martín, la catarata de Ahuashiyacu donde además podrá bañarse.</p></li></ul>, ,<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; list-style: outside none; text-align: justify;\"><li class=\"iti_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M19 10H9l2.71-3.29A.996.996 0 1 0 10.3 5.3c.03-.02-3.21 2.64-4.29 3.71-1.01.99-2 2-2 5 0 2 1 4 3 4h5c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h5c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1Z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Traslados desde y hacia el aeropuerto de Tarapoto.</p></li><li class=\"iti_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot