(499, 6, 'idpaquete', '48', '48,Escape a Tarapoto,04,03,si incluye, no incluye,<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; list-style: outside none;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Con este paquete turístico visitará los&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">4 lugares turísticos de Tarapoto</span>&nbsp;más conocidos: la Laguna Azul, Alto Mayo, Lamas y Catarata de Ahuashiyacu.</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Conocerá el único castillo de estilo medieval de toda la amazonía, el&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">Castillo de Lamas.</span></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M21 12 3 19l4-7-4-7 18 7z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1.1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Podrá bañarse en las cálidas aguas de la&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder;\">laguna azul</span>&nbsp;(20º de media) y navegar en bote.</p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: ur