lns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M19 10H9l2.71-3.29A.996.996 0 1 0 10.3 5.3c.03-.02-3.21 2.64-4.29 3.71-1.01.99-2 2-2 5 0 2 1 4 3 4h5c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h5c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1Z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Entradas.</p></li><li class=\"iti_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%231877F2\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;M19 10H9l2.71-3.29A.996.996 0 1 0 10.3 5.3c.03-.02-3.21 2.64-4.29 3.71-1.01.99-2 2-2 5 0 2 1 4 3 4h5c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h1c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1h5c.55 0 1-.45 1-1s-.45-1-1-1Z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Atención personalizada de 07:30 a.m a 08:30 p.m. en el teléfono +51 930 637 287</p></li></ul>,<ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; list-style: outside none; text-align: justify;\"><li class=\"iti_list\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 24 24\\&quot; fill=\\&quot;%23F34646\\&quot;><path d=\\&quot;m13.41 12 6.29-6.29c.94-.94-.48-2.35-1.41-1.41L12 10.59 5.71 4.3c-.93-.93-2.35.48-1.41 1.41L10.59 12 4.3 18.29c-.94.94.48 2.35 1.41 1.41L12 13.41c6.12 6.12 6.74 7.26 7.71 6.29a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41L13.42 12Z\\&quot;></path></svg>&quot;); font-size: 1em;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Las actividades opcionales de Kayak, moto acuática y canotaje en el recreo turístico el Caño.</p></li><li class=\"